law.text:
The bonds of any issue shall be payable solely from the property or receipts of the Authority, including, without limitation:
Fees, charges, or other revenues payable to the Authority;
Payments by financial institutions, insurance companies, or others pursuant to letters or lines of credit, policies of insurance, or purchase agreements;
Investment earnings from funds or accounts maintained pursuant to a bond resolution or trust agreement;
Proceeds of refunding bonds; and
Any other source authorized by law.
